Specificity makes the difference. There’s something in chiropractic called the “Flying 7”. 

This means chiropractors do the same 7 adjustments on everybody no matter who you are or what you have going on. 

Needless to say, this is not my philosophy or something that I think is best for the patient. I want to always find what is specifically going on for that patient, that issue and figure out what adjustments can best help get the body into a higher functioning state. #resultsmatter
